data.description: Spectacular Desert Retreat Home located in the Highly Desirable Sun City Shadow Hills, 55+, Gated Community!! This is the Very Popular,  2,147 SFT “San Benito” Model featuring 2 Lg Bedrooms, 3rd is a Convertible SpaceBonus/Den/Office Room, 2 Full Bathrooms. The home is an Entertainers Dream, known for Open Concept, High Ceilings, Eat-In Kitchen/Breakfast Bar w/ a Built-In Pantry that opens up to Lg Great Room w/ Recessed Lighting & Ceiling Fans throughout.  At the end of the day, Retreat to your Luxurious Primary Suite that comes complete w/ Lg Walk-In Closet, Duel Vanity Sink, Separate Walk-In Shower, Sunken Tub, Private Toilet & Separate Access to Backyard. Step outside & enjoy the Magnificent Mountain/Desert View while relaxing on your Covered Patio in your Private Backyard.  Huge 3 Car Garage w/ lots of Storage Space that enters through the Separate Indoor Laundry Rm. Enjoy Abundance of Natural Light & Spacious Living in this Well-Appointed Open Space Floorplan.   Embrace the Carefree Lifestyle of living in Sun City Shadow Hills!! Take advantage of the Communities Amenities such as Tennis,Shuffleboard,Bocce, Pickleball, 2 Fitness Centesr, Several Pools/Spas, 2 Club Houses, Restaurants & Shadow Hills Golf Club w/ 18 Hole Course and Newer Par 3 Course & 18 Hole Putting Course. The Community also offers a Billiards Hall, Ballroom,Library, Dog Park, Various Social Clubs to join such as Travel, Wine, Hiking, Cycling, Book Clubs & much, much more. Special Events to attend throughout the year. Explore Recreational Activities in nearby Palm Springs & the Coachella Valley. Must See, Must Have Home!!’
